properties.areaDesc: Green Bay North of line from Cedar River MI to Rock Island Passage
properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 10 at 4:35AM EST until January 12 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
waves 3 to 6 feet possible.

* WHERE...Green Bay North of line from Cedar River MI to Rock
Island Passage.

* WHEN...From Saturday afternoon through late Saturday night.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and waves.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM SATURDAY AFTERNOON THROUGH LATE SATURDAY NIGHT
